                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d463">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 839.00/1002.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">American Minister</gloss> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegrams—Paraphrases.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Santo Domingo</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1913-12-13">
                            <hi rend="italic">December 13, 1913</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>The agents arrived Thursday and have departed for their posts with detailed
                    instructions. The Department’s delegates arrived yesterday and will remain
                    here.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Sullivan</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
